#: app/templates/landing.html:561
msgid ""
"Enhancing field mapping efficiency and accuracy through seamless "
"coordination."
msgstr "Inganta inganci da daidaiton taswirar fili ta hanyar haɗin kai mai sauƙi."

#: app/templates/landing.html:565
